snippet.title: StarCraft 2 Wings of Liberty Intro Cinematic Full HD
snippet.description:
Here's the full ingame intro cinematic from StarCraft 2.

Recorded the Video with Fraps at 1920x1080 and converted it with Sony Vegas 9b Platinum Video shape didn't change due to the original cinematic already being in widescreen (think it's 2,35:1)~
